{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012VyZ8oatCvkLRqVxPBZyfV","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→---\n     2→id: \"001\"\n     3→title: Fix login SSO bug\n     4→status: in-progress\n     5→priority: high\n     6→effort: medium\n     7→type: bug\n     8→tags: [auth, urgent]\n     9→created: 2026-03-01\n    10→---\n    11→\n    12→# Fix login SSO bug\n    13→\n    14→## Objective\n    15→\n    16→Fix the login flow when users authenticate via SSO. Currently, the callback handler does not properly validate the SAML response, causing intermittent login failures for enterprise users.\n    17→\n    18→## Tasks\n    19→\n    20→- [x] Reproduce the bug with a test SSO provider\n    21→- [ ] Add SAML response validation in the callback handler\n    22→- [ ] Handle expired SSO sessions gracefully\n    23→- [ ] Add error logging for failed SSO attempts\n    24→\n    25→## Acceptance Criteria\n    26→\n    27→- SSO login works reliably with SAML 2.0 providers\n    28→- Expired sessions show a user-friendly error message\n    29→- Failed SSO attempts are logged with correlation IDs\n    30→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e0afeb34-0f98-4f84-96bd-d21485f3b5ea","uuid":"727d8d9e-a28a-4fcf-ac8b-b21dd794f40d","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/private/var/folders/50/9csqlcg54r1d9pb3b7dmtp300000gn/T/tmp.FH0XLaMD4i/tasks/001-fix-login-sso-bug.md","content":"---\nid: \"001\"\ntitle: Fix login SSO bug\nstatus: in-progress\npriority: high\neffort: medium\ntype: bug\ntags: [auth, urgent]\ncreated: 2026-03-01\n---\n\n# Fix login SSO bug\n\n## Objective\n\nFix the login flow when users authenticate via SSO. Currently, the callback handler does not properly validate the SAML response, causing intermittent login failures for enterprise users.\n\n## Tasks\n\n- [x] Reproduce the bug with a test SSO provider\n- [ ] Add SAML response validation in the callback handler\n- [ ] Handle expired SSO sessions gracefully\n- [ ] Add error logging for failed SSO attempts\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- SSO login works reliably with SAML 2.0 providers\n- Expired sessions show a user-friendly error message\n- Failed SSO attempts are logged with correlation IDs\n","numLines":30,"startLine":1,"totalLines":30}}}
